        <mxCell id="ZVHNjA796QK2NxNg57cw-1" value="Doing complicated security things is difficult. Doing it once right and reusing it is valuable.&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Package in a library for every service to use&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Run in on a shared proxy server every service to use&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Each service runs it on a proxy server&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
